    <section id="Stonehenge+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Stonehenge Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the Stonehenge project status, from the perspective of incubation. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="retired">The Stonehenge project retired on 2011-07-05</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>Stonehenge is a set of example applications for Service Oriented Architecture that spans languages and 
      	platforms and demonstrates best practices and interoperability.</p>
    </section>
